        "eyebrow": "Our Story",
        "title": "The Art Shop Hermanus",
        "text": "<p>Since 2006, The Art Shop Hermanus has served as a cornerstone of the Western Cape’s creative community. What began as a local retail space has grown into a trusted hub for artists, crafters, and visionaries across the region.<br/><br/>We specialize in high-end fine art supplies, focusing on a curated selection of both local and imported products. Our philosophy is simple: premium quality shouldn’t come with a premium barrier. We stretch our margins to ensure that the best tools remain affordable for every creator.<br/><br/>When you walk through our doors, you aren’t just a customer—you’re a peer. Our promise is a professional, helpful experience defined by a warm smile and a commitment to your craft. If we don’t have what you need on the floor, we’ll go above and beyond to find it for you.</p>",
